{"tid":420704,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係咪傷過既人都好難再信人？","createTime":"2017-10-01T15:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T13:04:40.000Z","uid":76695,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c2b2fd913c5a40a949772f7a36ad62ef4bd544","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:47:28.000Z","msg":"個種感覺<br />\n好似你放左成副心機落一個人到<br />\n但係可以咩預警都無 話散就散<br />\n<br />\n明明拍拖係兩個人既決定<br />\n點解分手可以係一個人話完就完？<br />\n<br />\n而從此之後<br />\n好似寧願做隻刺蝟<br />\n都唔想做比人拮傷果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89ebc21e60ff5fc963c79ea690f0e3b697efb78","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62110e67a7a6d2238a0caec629d1fb344683b485","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7b70aa6b530abb67fd85b320d827853faca89f","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce71d211e5fa89a6e8c69b6c67d7a6fd4c372b8","tid":420704,"uid":59307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:54:52.000Z","msg":"我個陣都係咁 <br />\n男朋友偷食 琴依加都覺得男人會咁<br />\n偷食完 我原諒左佢 佢仲要飛我<br />\n依幾年都冇信過男人"},{"pid":"8921b13fb634d1b2e5010c9f3d60bce897334fca","tid":420704,"uid":71422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:55:07.000Z","msg":"點比人傷都好 唔好變 唔好做衰人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少我仲堅持緊"},{"pid":"cd4e54b331199c7bc77143258f9d7aaaebe5658b","tid":420704,"uid":74894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"我ex都係話分手就分手，足足半年先放得低。到而家仲係好驚拍拖。"},{"pid":"f5104cbe8b9032efec7c3032284035080fb75824","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我ex都係話分手就分手，足足半年先放得低。到而家仲係好驚拍拖。</blockquote><br />\n我好怕我落左下一段感情會好似佢咁<br />\n因為唔夠愛而走hurt到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4ccd9fd42b247cb3f38a350f4493b6f57340a9","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點比人傷都好 唔好變 唔好做衰人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少我仲堅持緊</blockquote><br />\n原來隨便錯手 可毀了人一世"},{"pid":"37f615f98d7c9e306b26d73e2331e120cc9e4a1c","tid":420704,"uid":148701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:58:22.000Z","msg":"巴打，記得做好自己，要活得比佢好。"},{"pid":"de41b79ec8bf79ed50f50f0092071b19ecad8f53","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個陣都係咁 <br />\n男朋友偷食 琴依加都覺得男人會咁<br />\n偷食完 我原諒左佢 佢仲要飛我<br />\n依幾年都冇信過男人</blockquote><br />\n定係其實我地未遇到個好鐘意既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係唔知自己復元未"},{"pid":"335fbe24b29a86be94f32379ef0a826c9ed51538","tid":420704,"uid":92357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以傷害下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc599f9fd26a28fb9276d84015375a292bfb383e","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打，記得做好自己，要活得比佢好。</blockquote><br />\n佢hurt到我 令我成長<br />\n但係同時我覺得自己已經唔係一張白紙<br />\n好似對好多人都有防備既心<br />\n做唔到以前既自己"},{"pid":"fc53d3b7ee77a89d1959abd8d9a6ccd9b224b341","tid":420704,"uid":148701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人可以傷害下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實個感覺真係好慘好辛苦，最好都唔好比人傷害或傷害人"},{"pid":"a561c9242a85054642ee601b70c7978f0b12ddd1","tid":420704,"uid":74272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"天真有邪"},{"pid":"de61f443cb6339c92b72f1d1d6dbdcce8521e831","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人可以傷害下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心如果可以<br />\n我寧願無開始過<br />\n宜家反而唔知自己想點<br />\n人生目標又唔明確"},{"pid":"285b63d67d6bbe27d869d8da77334b294bf64e0d","tid":420704,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:01:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b627164f5978c0ef241288acdb5248eba0d51e6","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天真有邪</blockquote><br />\n巴打 呢首我聽到喊 真係第一次覺得有共鳴"},{"pid":"feb8ea1ca5bd1cb497d7eec54b5cecac7e39a031","tid":420704,"uid":148701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:02:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打，記得做好自己，要活得比佢好。</blockquote><br />\n佢hurt到我 令我成長<br />\n但係同時我覺得自己已經唔係一張白紙<br />\n好似對好多人都有防備既心<br />\n做唔到以前既自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁經一事，蔡一智，我都係咁，都係會變左好難攞個心出黎，變左會有時唔知自己想點&hellip;"},{"pid":"d58619898612bb533e9a6a3cb86afe3d7f6c69d9","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人可以傷害下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實個感覺真係好慘好辛苦，最好都唔好比人傷害或傷害人</blockquote><br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b7df0b858b235580bc7172381cf555b45b99b2","tid":420704,"uid":74894,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我ex都係話分手就分手，足足半年先放得低。到而家仲係好驚拍拖。</blockquote><br />\n我好怕我落左下一段感情會好似佢咁<br />\n因為唔夠愛而走hurt到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，果時佢話唔夠愛我，覺得一個人開心啲唔岩拍拖。一句就完左，唔再理我。但係過左兩個星期見到佢同另一個一齊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n真係hurt到爆炸，果段時間日日都好想斬人。和平有預料果啲分手唔可怕，冇啦啦被分手先係最恐怖。"},{"pid":"067fe3ee429b7099bd693faf598e6e26008767a7","tid":420704,"uid":148701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:03:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我ex都係話分手就分手，足足半年先放得低。到而家仲係好驚拍拖。</blockquote><br />\n我好怕我落左下一段感情會好似佢咁<br />\n因為唔夠愛而走hurt到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，果時佢話唔夠愛我，覺得一個人開心啲唔岩拍拖。一句就完左，唔再理我。但係過左兩個星期見到佢同另一個一齊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n真係hurt到爆炸，果段時間日日都好想斬人。和平有預料果啲分手唔可怕，冇啦啦被分手先係最恐怖。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel&hellip;"},{"pid":"ddd167f518abc12612d50471bdf553e05040f442","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係 比左處個ex之後比佢飛左 而家我咩人都唔想信</blockquote><br />\n又愛又恨？"},{"pid":"fc53e416f39dcea72c1d8868f33151125095d249","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:06:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打，記得做好自己，要活得比佢好。</blockquote><br />\n佢hurt到我 令我成長<br />\n但係同時我覺得自己已經唔係一張白紙<br />\n好似對好多人都有防備既心<br />\n做唔到以前既自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁經一事，蔡一智，我都係咁，都係會變左好難攞個心出黎，變左會有時唔知自己想點&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n你有無好似我咁 成個人講少左野 少左同人分享心事"},{"pid":"8f9080a77b2af27597e29e2f6a680af3fe0a51f9","tid":420704,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我ex都係話分手就分手，足足半年先放得低。到而家仲係好驚拍拖。</blockquote><br />\n我好怕我落左下一段感情會好似佢咁<br />\n因為唔夠愛而走hurt到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，果時佢話唔夠愛我，覺得一個人開心啲唔岩拍拖。一句就完左，唔再理我。但係過左兩個星期見到佢同另一個一齊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n真係hurt到爆炸，果段時間日日都好想斬人。和平有預料果啲分手唔可怕，冇啦啦被分手先係最恐怖。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel&hellip;</blockquote><br />\nme too...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsudden death既感覺真係好差<br />\n宜家恢復正常？"},{"pid":"6535eb33eeedd0430f9707fb9c1b208671da4e2c","tid":420704,"uid":148701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打，記得做好自己，要活得比佢好。</blockquote><br />\n佢hurt到我 令我成長<br />\n但係同時我覺得自己已經唔係一張白紙<br />\n好似對好多人都有防備既心<br />\n做唔到以前既自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁經一事，蔡一智，我都係咁，都係會變左好難攞個心出黎，變左會有時唔知自己想點&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n你有無好似我咁 成個人講少左野 少左同人分享心事</blockquote><br />\n我唔知，我直情比人話變左另一個人，同啲fd講野都少左，到而家都唔太會同人講自己野"},{"pid":"a0a2a904aee143d1c9d9ae99e509d5ddee4504c2","tid":420704,"uid":74894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:10:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我ex都係話分手就分手，足足半年先放得低。到而家仲係好驚拍拖。</blockquote><br />\n我好怕我落左下一段感情會好似佢咁<br />\n因為唔夠愛而走hurt到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，果時佢話唔夠愛我，覺得一個人開心啲唔岩拍拖。一句就完左，唔再理我。但係過左兩個星期見到佢同另一個一齊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n真係hurt到爆炸，果段時間日日都好想斬人。和平有預料果啲分手唔可怕，冇啦啦被分手先係最恐怖。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel&hellip;</blockquote><br />\nme too...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsudden death既感覺